reviewText: Beautiful pictures, well-versed Javanese, well-written subs. Beautiful wayang-based metaphors. Can get too artsy/weird for some people at times, but it wasn't there for nothing--it was a theatrical/stylistic film (rather than narrative) after all.
Again, I am using bits and pieces of this video for my mythology class, so I am using only what I needed.  It was a video I needed, not necessarily one I wanted or would go out and buy for myself.
